data.description: INSTANT EQUITY! This 4 bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage is priced well below market. It needs flooring, paint, and minor cosmetic upgrades. This is the perfect opportunity for an investor or owner occupant to update a home to their specifications and end up with equity day one. Roof, foundation, electrical, HVAC, and plumbing are believed to be in good condition. Appliances, cabinets, fixtures are all in good working order. Most 1 story homes in this area are missing the critical 4th bedroom. The master retreat has a large bathroom with a separate tub and shower. This floor plan is open and inviting. Newer french door leading out to a small covered patio. Landscaping is in good condition so no need to invest a lot of money to have nice curb appeal. Book an appointment today and make this house your home!
